name: 1996 Trippy Caves (Rainbow Abstracts)
description: My first trip on psychedelics my friends decided to take me to haunted houses on my birthday. They had no clue 30 minutes prior I had dropped two tabs of acid. Surprisingly I made caves deep in our planet a comedy club instead of fright night. By the time our tour was up the guide was ready to gag me just to get a word of cautIon in.
